✗ More Upfront Design

✗ Relational Modeling Discipline

---

# Enforcement

Structured platform data must be stored in PostgreSQL.

Do not use:

MongoDB

Redis

Qdrant

as primary transactional storage.

---

Redis is not a database of record.

Qdrant is not a database of record.

MinIO is not a database of record.

PostgreSQL remains the authoritative source.

